                     <interp inst="t18150510-42-verdict258" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing, but not in the dwelling-house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18150510-42-punish259" type="punishmentDescription">
